short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Chrome and Firefox devtools extension for debugging FicusJS applications

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This extension provides a panel in the elements inspector for viewing FicusJS web components. When selecting `Inspect element` the FicusJS panel will show the component props, computed properties and state of the component.
